  "description": "Tarot decks were historically used for card games before being widely used for divinatory readings.\nThese games are typically trick-taking and use the major arcana as trumps. Different regional variants exist, often grouped under \u0026ldquo;tarot\u0026rdquo; or \u0026ldquo;tarock\u0026rdquo; game traditions.\n",
